short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract all mobile numbers starting with +91 from a webpage.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract all mobile numbers starting with +91 from a webpage. To start just download this extension and enable it. Then open web page where you want to copy numbers and click on "extract" all numbers will be shown below. Once you complete it, a button to copy all numbers in clipboard will appear. You can click on it to copy and then paste it in notepad or any other place.
